<div class="tb"><h1>How do you show a twitter stream during the event?</h1>
        <ul class="navigation byline">
            <li><a class="nolink">Posted by </a><a href="../../profile/MattSteele">Matt Steele</a><a class="nolink"> on January 25, 2012 at 10:31pm in </a><a href="../../group/organizers-hosts">Organizers/Hosts</a></li>
