            <div class="description">
                                <div class="xg_user_generated">
                    <p>How have you showcased a twitter feed for the coderetreats you've hosted?</p>
<p></p>
<p>It'd be nice to have a projector showing the #coderetreat feed, and while I assume there are better options than manually refreshing Twitter's search page, I don't know what they are. Any suggestions?</p>                </div>
