                        <div class="description" id="desc_6456126Comment7865"><div class="xg_user_generated"><p>Hi,</p>
<p>we showcased the twitter feed with @peppertw,Â <a rel=nofollow href="http://peppertweet.com/" target="_blank">http://peppertweet.com/</a>.</p>
<p>It's a pet project written by me and other developers/designers in Italy.</p>
<p>The project isn't open sourced yet, we have still have work to do, but if you need it we can provide you an hosted installation for your event.Â </p>
<p>The plus is that it streams and shows also photos inside a tweet and you can collect them for future use.<br/>We use it for collecting Global Code Retreat photos (soon available)</p>
<p>You can see an example of the latest event we supported: <a rel=nofollow href="http://uan12.peppertweet.com" target="_blank">http://uan12.peppertweet.com</a> and <a rel=nofollow href="http://uan12.peppertweet.com/single" target="_blank">http://uan12.peppertweet.com/single</a></p>
